## Project\
\
This is the official website for SQ General PLT.\
\
SQ General PLT provides two main service pillars:\
\
1. Asset Planning and Estate Administration\
   - Will writing\
   - Personal trust planning\
   - Business / company trust planning\
   - Probate and Letters of Administration support\
   - Asset unfreezing and distribution assistance\
\
2. General Insurance\
   - Motor insurance\
   - Home / fire insurance\
   - Personal accident insurance\
   - Travel insurance\
   - Business insurance\
   - Public liability insurance\
   - Employer liability insurance\
   - Contractor / engineering insurance\
   - Other general insurance products\
\
The website should help potential clients understand the company\'92s services and contact SQ General PLT through WhatsApp, phone, email, or enquiry form.\
\
