\
Position SQ General PLT as a professional advisory and service provider for:\
\
- Asset succession planning\
- Estate administration support\
- Trust planning\
- General insurance arrangement\
- Personal and business risk protection\
\
Do not describe SQ General PLT as a law firm unless specifically instructed.\
